         PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089) before NuGet has restored
         GHIElectronics.TinyCLR.Core.props (which sets NoStdLib=true). That
         BCL reference caches into obj/<Config>/<name>.csproj.AssemblyReference.cache
