         referenced multiple times with different versions". Setting it
         directly in the template guarantees TinyCLR mscorlib is the only
         one resolved, regardless of NuGet restore timing. -->
    <NoStdLib>true</NoStdLib>
    <AddAdditionalExplicitAssemblyReferences>false</AddAdditionalExplicitAssemblyReferences>
    <!-- Default C# language version for new TinyCLR projects. net4.8 defaults to
