         fires before NuGet has populated packages\ (packages.config projects
         don't auto-restore on build), Core.props is skipped, no mscorlib is in
         scope, and the user sees a flood of CS0518/CS0234 errors in a file
         they never wrote. Disabling generation makes Rebuild robust against
         NuGet restore timing. -->
